channel.title: Help... Auto restarter
channel.description:
Well I just bought a dedicated host after my vps's failed horribly.
It has been going fine for the past two to three days, but recently on my auto restarter which is every 45 minutes, when it restarts it says "Server already in use". Can someone please help?
Thanks.
